body:
### Welcome to use Secret Notebook
Secret Notebook is an application to record your personal information safely. You can write note with attached photos. You can create more than one secret account to save different kind of information. You can switch account freely and this makes your information very secret.

If you have any question or advice, please send E-Mail to mint@vip.qq.com
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
